rows.label: tlk000009_msg0001
rows.name: Jakolo's Inn, how may I help you?

rows.label: tlk000009_msg0002
rows.name: Do you happen to be the Tora party?

rows.label: tlk000009_msg0003
rows.name:
Ah, grand.
Muimui mentioned you'd be coming.

rows.label: tlk000009_msg0004
rows.name:
It so happens we're offering a special
rate today.

rows.label: tlk000009_msg0006
rows.name:
We're also proud to offer one of the
finest open-air baths. Feel free to use
them at your leisure.

rows.label: tlk000009_msg0007
rows.name:
You'll be wanting to take in the sights
of Alba Margen, I imagine.

rows.label: tlk000009_msg0008
rows.name:
Just pop back whenever you need
a good night's rest.
